title: OST Vanishing Point 1971
description:
Soundtrack and some pictures from the super-cool 1971 classic car movie "Vanishing Point"....the music is fantastic, I only wish I had my own Challenger too...

Songs:

Sing Out For Jesus - Big Mama Thornton
The Girl Got It Together - Bobby Doyle
You Got To Believe - Bonnie, Delaney And Friends
So Tired - Eve
Freedom Of Expression - J.B. Pickers
Super Soul Theme - J.B. Pickers
Welcome To Nevada - Jerry Reed
Were Do We Go From Here - Jimmy Walker
Nobody Know - Kim & Dave
Mississippi Queen - Mountain
Over Me - Segarini And Bishop



Keep sharing and enjoy these songs!
